description: Experience breathtaking views of the Seaport from this sleek and modern top-floor unit on South Boston's vibrant West Side. With 2 spacious bedrooms, 2 full baths, a private balcony, and a full-size garage parking spot, this home truly has it all. Luxury features throughout include Viking appliances, new washer/dryer, custom shades and piped in gas on the balcony for a grill. Both bedrooms are generously sized with one featuring an ensuite bath. Seaport Crossing is a boutique elevator building, newly constructed in 2013. It offers a garage, elevator, expansive common rooftop patio, a fitness center and security system. With significant development planned for the block and its proximity to the Seaport, this property is not only an exceptional place to call home, but a smart investment. Located less than a mile from the shops and restaurants of Seaport Blvd and Northern Ave, Southie's bustling W Broadway and the Red Line T, the location is unmatched! Easy to show.
